<HL>
   Wal-Mart Set
   To Eliminate
   Reps, Brokers
   ----
   By Karen Blumenthal
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/02/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A3
</SO>
